\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  He began to strategize a route to She tied up the , then asked, with a look of genuine concern for the foolish, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why did you jump into a lizard pit?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I never jumped into that pit,\u8221\'94 Mandri said defensively. \u8220\'93Moto threw me in.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s not what Moto told me.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, he lied.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93He also told me you killed yourself and that\u8217\'92s why we found you dead in the Junei hills.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I never told him how I died. He was lying to you.\u8221\'94}
